General.Name: LMK Group AB
General.Description: LMK Group AB (publ) supplies and delivers meal kits to the customer's front door in Sweden, Norway, and Denmark. It operates under the Linas Matkasse, Godtlevert, Adams Matkasse, and RetNemt brand names. The company was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Sundbyberg, Sweden.
